https://ahrefs.com/backlink-checker -- see who's linking back to a given site 
https://www.semrush.com/analytics/traffic/ -- see the top performing pages for any site
https://archive.org/web/web.php -- archive any page on the web
https://www.seoreviewtools.com/website-traffic-checker/ -- estimates inbound/outbound traffic numbers on a site

